case_name: Hippie-named patient with lower back pain seeking baseball return
case_description: Patient Zippity Doodaa (given by hippie parents) presents with stable lower back pain. Currently taking omeprazole 20mg daily. Has severe penicillin allergy (anaphylaxis). Goal is to return to playing baseball without back pain.
messages: that's really it man, I had hippie parents and I have to live with it every day now
I will essentially die if I take penecillins
I want to play baseball again, free from back pain
